trans-unit.source: Represents the collection of extensibility elements used by the XML Web service.
This class cannot be inherited.
This collection can either contain instances of classes deriving from <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension>, or instances of the <xref:System.Xml.XmlElement> class.
trans-unit.target: 此集合可以包含衍生自類別的執行個體<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension>，或執行個體<xref:System.Xml.XmlElement>類別。

trans-unit.source: In a derived class, <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension> class allows users to define extensibility elements in addition to those defined in the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) specification.
trans-unit.target: 在衍生類別中，<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension>類別可讓使用者定義除了 Web 服務描述語言 (WSDL) 規格中定義的擴充性項目。

trans-unit.source: Use these in your <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection> if you know in advance the type of extensibility element you want to make.
trans-unit.target: 在中使用這些程式<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection>如果您事先知道您想要的擴充性項目的型別。

trans-unit.source: Use an <xref:System.Xml.XmlElement> when you do not know the format of an element in advance.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Xml.XmlElement>時您不知道項目的格式事先。

trans-unit.source: The object of which this collection is a member.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection" /> class.

Since many of the classes in the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description> namespace expose an `Extensions` property representing a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection>, the constructor assigns a parent object corresponding to the level within the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) hierarchy where the current `ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection` is nested.
trans-unit.target: 自的類別中的許多<xref:System.Web.Services.Description>命名空間公開`Extensions`屬性代表<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection>，建構函式會指派對應到 Web 服務描述語言 (WSDL) 階層內的層級的父物件，目前`ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection`巢狀。

trans-unit.source: For more information about WSDL, see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: 如需有關 WSDL 的詳細資訊，請參閱規格的http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" />, passed by reference, to add to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection" />.

Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" /> to the end of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection" />.
The zero-based index where the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" /> has been added.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" /> for which to check collection membership.

Returns a value indicating whether the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" /> is a member of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection" />.
<see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" /> is a member of the collection; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
An array of type <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" /> serving as the destination of the copy action.
The zero-based index at which to start placing the copied collection.

Copies the entire <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection" /> into a one-dimensional array of type <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" />, starting at the specified zero-based index of the target array.
Searches the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection" /> and returns the first member of the collection specified by the parameter passed in.
A <see cref="T:System.Type" /> for which to search the collection.
Searches the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection" /> and returns the first element of the specified derived <see cref="T:System.Type" />.
If the search is successful, an object of the specified <see cref="T:System.Type" />; otherwise, <see langword="null" />.
This method searches the collection in index order, and returns only the matching element with the lowest-numbered index.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會在集合中搜尋索引順序，並傳回僅索引編號最低的符合項目。

trans-unit.source: The name of the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlElement" /> to be found.
The XML namespace URI of the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlElement" /> to be found.
Searches the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection" /> for a member with the specified name and namespace URI.
If the search is successful, an <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlElement" />; otherwise, <see langword="null" />.
This method searches the collection in index order, and returns the first <xref:System.Xml.XmlElement> that meets the criteria of the two parameters.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會在集合中搜尋索引順序，並傳回第一個<xref:System.Xml.XmlElement>符合兩個參數的準則。

trans-unit.source: Searches the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection" /> for all members of the collection specified by the parameter passed in.
A <see cref="T:System.Type" /> for which to search the collection.
Searches the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection" /> and returns an array of all elements of the specified <see cref="T:System.Type" />.
An array of <see cref="T:System.Object" /> instances representing all collection members of the specified type.
The array returned is empty if the search is unsuccessful.
trans-unit.target: 傳回的陣列是空的搜尋時失敗。

trans-unit.source: The XML name attribute of the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlElement" /> objects to be found.
The XML namespace URI attribute of the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlElement" /> objects to be found.
Searches the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection" /> and returns an array of all members with the specified name and namespace URI.
An array of <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlElement" /> instances.
The array returned is empty if the search is unsuccessful.
trans-unit.target: 傳回的陣列是空的搜尋時失敗。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" /> for which to search in the collection.
Searches for the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" /> and returns the zero-based index of the first instance with the collection.
The zero-based index of the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" />, or -1 if the element was not found in the collection.
The zero-based index at which to insert the <c>extension</c> parameter.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" /> to add to the collection.

Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" /> to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection" /> at the specified zero-based index.
If the number of items in the collection already equals the collection's capacity, the capacity is doubled by automatically reallocating the internal array before the new element is inserted.
trans-unit.target: 如果已經在集合中的項目數等於集合的容量，容量加倍插入新項目之前，會自動重新配置內部的陣列。

trans-unit.source: If the `index` parameter is equal to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>, the `extension` parameter is added to the end of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection>.
trans-unit.target: 如果`index`參數等於<xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>、`extension`參數加入至結尾<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection>。

trans-unit.source: The elements after the insertion point move down to accommodate the new element.
trans-unit.target: 向下移動以容納新項目插入點後的項目。

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> parameter is less than zero.
\- or -
The <paramref name="index" /> parameter is greater than <see cref="P:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count" />.
An object, either of type <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlElement" /> or <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" /> to check for use by the import process.
Returns a value indicating whether the specified object is used by the import process when the extensibility element is imported into the XML Web service.
<see langword="true" /> if the <paramref name="item" /> parameter is used; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.

This method checks whether the `item` parameter is an <xref:System.Xml.XmlElement> or a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension> (or a derived class) before determining whether it is supported by the XML Web service.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會檢查是否`item`參數是<xref:System.Xml.XmlElement>或<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension>（或衍生的類別） 然後再判斷它是否支援的 XML Web 服務。

trans-unit.source: An object, either of type <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlElement" /> or <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" />, to check whether it is necessary.
Returns a value indicating whether the specified object is necessary for the operation of the XML Web service.
<see langword="true" /> if the <paramref name="item" /> parameter is required; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
The zero-based index of the member whose value is modified or returned.

The value of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" />.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" /> to remove from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection" />.

Removes the first occurrence of the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension" /> from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection" />.
